# game/story.rpy:6
translate spanish story_615ae8ae:

    # "Hey everyone, morbiusgreen here."
    "Hola a todos, soy morbiusgreen."

# game/story.rpy:7
translate spanish story_de11e0a3:

    # "As this is my very first attempt at a mod/story, I'm sorry for any mistakes I may have made."
    "Como es mi primer intento de crear un mod o una historia, os pido disculpas por cualquier error que haya podido cometer."

# game/story.rpy:8
translate spanish story_401e8f43:

    # "In order to better enjoy the mod, headphones/earphones are encouraged for a more immersive experience."
    "Para disfrutar mejor del mod, os recomiendo usar auriculares para conseguir una experiencia más inmersiva."

# game/story.rpy:9
translate spanish story_e2c2950c:

    # "Anyway, enjoy {i}Doki Doki: World of Dreams Act 1{/i}."
    "En fin, disfrutad de {i}Doki Doki: World of Dreams Acto 1{/i}."

# game/story.rpy:23
translate spanish story_aa924373:

    # "Aaah...it's a nice night. Not too cold, but just warm enough to enjoy a nice cold one before bed."
    "Ahhh... Qué buena noche. No hace demasiada rasca, la temperatura es ideal para disfrutar de un refresco fresquito antes de dormir."

# game/story.rpy:24
translate spanish story_aa79aa7e:

    # "I crack open my soda can and take a sip, enjoying the peace and quiet for once."
    "Abro mi lata de refresco y le doy un sorbo, disfrutando de la paz y la tranquilidad por una vez."

# game/story.rpy:25
translate spanish story_28b29c83:

    # "Mom and Dad aren't home tonight. They've taken their second honeymoon to the beaches of Hawaii."
    "Mamá y papá no están en casa esta noche. Se han ido de segunda luna de miel a las playas de Hawái."

# game/story.rpy:26
translate spanish story_116b40e0:

    # "I love my parents, but I do like a quiet house more often than not."
    "Quiero a mis padres, pero, las cosas como son, me gusta que la casa esté tranquila."

# game/story.rpy:27
translate spanish story_6c805dee:

    # "I {i}am{/i} glad that they're off enjoying their time together."
    "La verdad es que me alegra que se hayan ido a disfrutar de su tiempo juntos."

# game/story.rpy:28
translate spanish story_b6daf15a:

    # "As much as I like the quiet of being alone, Mom and Dad make having a relationship look amazing."
    "Por mucho que me guste la tranquilidad de estar solo, mamá y papá hacen que tener una relación parezca una pasada."

# game/story.rpy:29
translate spanish story_9530536f:

    # "They have fights sure, but their anger always dissipates after they cool down."
    "Tienen sus peleas, claro, pero el enfado siempre se les pasa cuando se calman."

# game/story.rpy:30
translate spanish story_aa0ff248:

    # "I've never seen a happier couple."
    "Nunca he visto a una pareja más feliz."

# game/story.rpy:31
translate spanish story_ec5108fa:

    # "I take another sip."
    "Le doy otro sorbo."

# game/story.rpy:32
translate spanish story_1c549c3a:

    # "Ah well...the quiet is still nice..."
    "Ah, bueno... El silencio sigue siendo agradable..."

# game/story.rpy:33
translate spanish story_cb69072e:

    # "After a while, I finish the soda, stretch and head inside."
    "Un rato después, me termino el refresco, me desperezo y entro en casa."

# game/story.rpy:39
translate spanish story_ffb3353d:

    # "I sit down on the couch, wrap myself up in a warm blanket and turn on the TV."
    "Me siento en el sofá, me envuelvo en una manta calentita y enciendo la tele."

# game/story.rpy:40
translate spanish story_7e46bfab:

    # "I browse through the stations and find an old show to watch."
    "Hago zapping por los canales y encuentro un programa viejo para ver."

# game/story.rpy:41
translate spanish story_2041a696:

    # "As I sit there, I get a text from Dad."
    "Mientras estoy ahí sentado, recibo un mensaje de papá."

# game/story.rpy:42
translate spanish story_bacf9bb5:

    # "It's a selfie of him and Mom at the beach with the tagline “{i}Miss you honey!{/i}”"
    "Es un selfi de él y mamá en la playa con el texto: '{i}¡Te echamos de menos, cariño!{/i}'."

# game/story.rpy:43
translate spanish story_6940aa0e:

    # "Heh, they look pretty happy."
    "Je, se les ve muy felices."

# game/story.rpy:44
translate spanish story_a30966d2:

    # "I go back to watching TV."
    "Vuelvo a centrarme en la tele."

# game/story.rpy:45
translate spanish story_f7a71778:

    # "Mmm...the blanket is nice and cozy..."
    "Mmm... La manta es muy suave y calentita..."

# game/story.rpy:51
translate spanish story_05229b8c:

    # "I think I'm gonna...nod off..."
    "Creo que me voy a... quedar frito..."

# game/story.rpy:57
translate spanish story_0494db3c:

    # "Night..."
    "Buenas noches..."

# game/story.rpy:76
translate spanish story_841157c2:

    # cm2 "Mmmm...another morning."
    cm2 "Mmmm... Ya es de día."

# game/story.rpy:77
translate spanish story_e752062f:

    # cm2 "Thank goodness it's Saturday."
    cm2 "Menos mal que es sábado."

# game/story.rpy:78
translate spanish story_0a4275ba:

    # cm2 "I sit up and stretch, looking out at the nice weekend weather."
    cm2 "Me incorporo y me desperezo mientras contemplo el buen tiempo que hace este fin de semana."

# game/story.rpy:79
translate spanish story_e953a0aa:

    # cm "Ugh...yesterday's test was so...not cool."
    cm "Uf... El examen de ayer no me salió... nada bien."

# game/story.rpy:84
translate spanish story_663ed464:

    # cm2 "I head downstairs to grab some breakfast."
    cm2 "Bajo a la cocina a preparar algo para desayunar."

# game/story.rpy:85
translate spanish story_de4cfbb2:

    # cm2 "I don't hear anyone else around, but I see a note from my mom."
    cm2 "No oigo a nadie más en casa, pero veo una nota de mi madre."

# game/story.rpy:86
translate spanish story_813dd26f:

    # mom2 "GOOD MORNING MEIJI. DAD AND I WENT TO VISIT AIKO. PLEASE TRY AND AT LEAST TAKE A WALK TODAY."
    mom2 "BUENOS DÍAS, MEIJI. PAPÁ Y YO HEMOS IDO A VISITAR A AIKO. POR FAVOR, INTENTA AL MENOS DAR UN PASEO HOY."

# game/story.rpy:87
translate spanish story_86f409e6:

    # mom2 "HAVE A GOOD DAY. WE'LL BE BACK LATE TONIGHT. YOUR DAD AND I LOVE YOU! ~MOM"
    mom2 "QUE TENGAS UN BUEN DÍA. VOLVEREMOS TARDE ESTA NOCHE. ¡TU PADRE Y YO TE QUEREMOS MUCHO! MAMÁ."

# game/story.rpy:88
translate spanish story_84162557:

    # cm2 "Oh geez..."
    cm2 "Madre mía..."

# game/story.rpy:89
translate spanish story_2b27d6e4:

    # cm2 "Mom can be such a worrywart sometimes. It's embarrassing."
    cm2 "A veces, mamá se preocupa demasiado. Qué vergüenza."

# game/story.rpy:90
translate spanish story_bca8a8ec:

    # cm2 "I leave the note and look in the fridge for something to eat."
    cm2 "Dejo la nota y busco algo de comer en la nevera."

# game/story.rpy:91
translate spanish story_6ecb8640:

    # cm2 "I decide on some cereal."
    cm2 "Me decanto por unos cereales."

# game/story.rpy:92
translate spanish story_f4a4bc7e:

    # cm2 "When I'm done eating, I head back upstairs."
    cm2 "Cuando termino de desayunar, vuelvo arriba."

# game/story.rpy:97
translate spanish story_eb7125e9:

    # cm "Aaah...time to relax."
    cm "Aaah... Hora de relajarse."

# game/story.rpy:98
translate spanish story_b37120f2:

    # cm2 "I grab the new manga I've been reading and lay back on my bed."
    cm2 "Cojo el manga nuevo que he estado leyendo y me tumbo en la cama."

# game/story.rpy:99
translate spanish story_c2a74290:

    # cm2 "I get so into it, I lose track of time."
    cm2 "Me engancho tanto que pierdo la noción del tiempo."

# game/story.rpy:100
translate spanish story_7f2f9766:

    # u "...Lalalala!"
    u "... ¡Lalalala!"

# game/story.rpy:101
translate spanish story_9e7740c0:

    # cm2 "I can't help but hear the voice of a girl singing to herself from outside."
    cm2 "No puedo evitar oír la voz de una chica canturreando afuera."

# game/story.rpy:103
translate spanish story_fcb98469:

    # cm2 "I look out the window to see who it is."
    cm2 "Miro por la ventana para ver de quién se trata."

# game/story.rpy:109
translate spanish story_8e91f014:

    # cm2 "I see an annoying girl skipping down the road, smiling like she's totally oblivious to any attention she might draw to herself."
    cm2 "Veo a una chica muy pesada dando saltitos por la calle. Sonríe, como si fuera totalmente ajena a la atención que pueda llamar."

# game/story.rpy:110
translate spanish story_6df398e9:

    # cm "Oh, it's Sayori."
    cm "Ah, es Sayori."

# game/story.rpy:112
translate spanish story_285b8212:

    # cm2 "That girl is Sayori, my neighbor and good friend since we were children."
    cm2 "Esa chica es Sayori, mi vecina y buena amiga desde que éramos niños."

# game/story.rpy:113
translate spanish story_409f1bc4:

    # cm2 "We used to walk to school together, but starting around high school she would oversleep more and more frequently, and I would get tired of waiting up."
    cm2 "Solíamos ir juntos al instituto, pero al empezar bachillerato empezó a quedarse dormida cada vez más a menudo, y yo me harté de esperarla."

# game/story.rpy:114
translate spanish story_dd1c7dd5:

    # cm2 "I wonder where she's off too."
    cm2 "Me pregunto adónde irá."

# game/story.rpy:116
translate spanish story_c7efda7b:

    # cm2 "Her phone rings."
    cm2 "Le suena el móvil."

# game/story.rpy:117
translate spanish story_2b8853ff:

    # cm2 "I watch as she stops and pulls it out."
    cm2 "Veo cómo se detiene y lo saca."

# game/story.rpy:118
translate spanish story_81a48e97:

    # s 2hn "Hello?"
    s 2hn "¿Sí?"

# game/story.rpy:120
translate spanish story_758d7c8c:

    # s 4hr "Hi!"
    s 4hr "¡Hola!"

# game/story.rpy:121
translate spanish story_1936d55a:

    # s 1hx "No, I just got up."
    s 1hx "No, me acabo de levantar."

# game/story.rpy:122
translate spanish story_2e4e01f2:

    # s 1hc "We're still having that club meeting at noon, right?"
    s 1hc "Aún tenemos la reunión del club al mediodía, ¿verdad?"

# game/story.rpy:123
translate spanish story_20fea013:

    # s 1hb "..."
    s 1hb "..."

# game/story.rpy:125
translate spanish story_4f038dae:

    # s 4hr "Yep! I'll be there in a little bit!"
    s 4hr "¡Sí! ¡Estaré ahí en un rato!"

# game/story.rpy:126
translate spanish story_bb303c90:

    # s 4hx "See you soon! Bye!"
    s 4hx "¡Nos vemos! ¡Adiós!"

# game/story.rpy:129
translate spanish story_77a51748:

    # cm2 "Sayori hangs up and skips off down the street."
    cm2 "Sayori cuelga y se aleja dando saltitos por la calle."

# game/story.rpy:136
translate spanish story_79711b06:

    # cm2 "Sayori is Vice President of the Literature Club."
    cm2 "Sayori es la vicepresidenta del club de literatura."

# game/story.rpy:137
translate spanish story_76be901e:

    # cm2 "Not that I was ever aware that she had any interest in literature."
    cm2 "No es que yo supiera que tuviera algún interés en la literatura."

# game/story.rpy:138
translate spanish story_a70f2523:

    # cm2 "In fact, I'm 99%% sure she only did it because she thought it would be fun to help start a new club."
    cm2 "De hecho, estoy seguro al 99%% de que solo lo hizo porque pensó que sería divertido ayudar a crear un club nuevo."

# game/story.rpy:139
translate spanish story_f8ac9a72:

    # cm2 "Since she was the first one to show interest after the one who proposed the club, she inherited the title \"Vice President\"."
    cm2 "Como fue la primera en mostrar interés después de quien propuso fundar el club, heredó el título de vicepresidenta."

# game/story.rpy:140
translate spanish story_4f11e11f:

    # cm2 "That said, my interest in literature is guaranteed to be even less."
    cm2 "Dicho esto, os aseguro que mi interés por la literatura es aún menor."

# game/story.rpy:141
translate spanish story_161611ed:

    # cm2 "Unless you count manga. Because manga is literature!"
    cm2 "A menos que cuentes el manga. ¡Porque el manga es literatura!"

# game/story.rpy:142
translate spanish story_4d1798cf:

    # cm2 "I grab my manga and continue reading until my stomach rumbles, telling me it's lunch time."
    cm2 "Cojo el manga y sigo leyendo hasta que me rugen las tripas, avisándome de que es hora de comer."

# game/story.rpy:147
translate spanish story_86295b01:

    # cm2 "I head downstairs and find some cup ramen in the cupboard."
    cm2 "Bajo a la cocina y encuentro un bote de ramen instantáneo en el armario."

# game/story.rpy:148
translate spanish story_5841a35c:

    # cm2 "After boiling the water, I let the noodles sit while I find a soda to drink."
    cm2 "Después de hervir el agua, dejo reposar los fideos mientras busco un refresco."

# game/story.rpy:149
translate spanish story_71758e15:

    # cm2 "I finish lunch and head back up to my room."
    cm2 "Termino de comer y vuelvo a mi habitación."

# game/story.rpy:154
translate spanish story_22a874cf:

    # cm "Ah, the sun's coming in."
    cm "Ah, está entrando el sol."

# game/story.rpy:159
translate spanish story_bcb01806:

    # cm2 "I close the shades and find some anime to watch."
    cm2 "Cierro las persianas y busco algún anime para ver."

# game/story.rpy:160
translate spanish story_d0b89384:

    # cm2 "The hours pass in a blur."
    cm2 "Las horas se me pasan volando."

# game/story.rpy:161
translate spanish story_75459210:

    # cm2 "I look at my phone a bit later and notice that it's almost ten at night."
    cm2 "Miro el móvil un rato después y me doy cuenta de que son casi las diez de la noche."

# game/story.rpy:162
translate spanish story_654ca20d:

    # cm "Huh, guess I should sleep."
    cm "Hala, supongo que debería irme a dormir."

# game/story.rpy:163
translate spanish story_25e8cacb:

    # cm2 "I turn off the TV and get ready for bed."
    cm2 "Apago la tele y me preparo para ir a la cama."

# game/story.rpy:168
translate spanish story_ed24f28d:

    # cm "Just one more day of the blessed weekend..."
    cm "Solo un día más de este bendito fin de semana..."

# game/story.rpy:169
translate spanish story_aeaaee1e:

    # cm2 "I yawn and fall asleep slowly."
    cm2 "Bostezo y me quedo dormido poco a poco."

# game/story.rpy:210
translate spanish story_b9861df4:

    # "I groan. The alarm next to me is blaring in my ear nonstop."
    "Suelto un quejido. La alarma que tengo al lado me suena en el oído sin parar."

# game/story.rpy:211
translate spanish story_c5cd4c59:

    # "What happened last night?"
    "¿Qué pasó anoche?"

# game/story.rpy:212
translate spanish story_33c80b74:

    # "Let's see...I spent the evening alone since Mom and Dad are away."
    "A ver... Pasé la noche solo, ya que mamá y papá están fuera."

# game/story.rpy:213
translate spanish story_3883e0b7:

    # "My memory is hazy after that..."
    "A partir de ahí, mis recuerdos son borrosos..."

# game/story.rpy:214
translate spanish story_836c8a07:

    # "Did I pass out on the couch? Or did I make it to bed?"
    "¿Me quedé frito en el sofá? ¿O conseguí llegar a la cama?"

# game/story.rpy:215
translate spanish story_80ea2f70:

    # "Argh, that alarm! Time to shut you up!"
    "¡Argh, la jodida alarma! ¡Es hora de hacerte callar!"

# game/story.rpy:216
translate spanish story_21baa91f:

    # "In my half-asleep state, I reach over to turn the alarm off."
    "Medio dormido, estiro el brazo para apagar la alarma."

# game/story.rpy:217
translate spanish story_1c2cb25e:

    # "As I do so, I realize that I didn't set an alarm the night before."
    "Al hacerlo, me doy cuenta de que la noche anterior no puse ninguna alarma."

# game/story.rpy:218
translate spanish story_efa6eec6:

    # "I never set alarms in the first place."
    "Para empezar, yo nunca pongo alarmas."

# game/story.rpy:219
translate spanish story_12df7a9a:

    # "I sit up and look around the room, only to realize it's completely dark."
    "Me incorporo y echo un vistazo a la habitación, solo para darme cuenta de que está completamente a oscuras."

# game/story.rpy:220
translate spanish story_efe388a3:

    # mc "What the hell-? What happened last night? Am I sick or something?"
    mc "¿Qué narices...? ¿Qué pasó anoche? ¿Estoy enfermo o algo así?"

# game/story.rpy:221
translate spanish story_65b3b05f:

    # "I try to feel for my phone which I normally keep on the nightstand to my left."
    "Intento palpar en busca de mi móvil, que normalmente dejo en la mesita de noche a mi izquierda."

# game/story.rpy:222
translate spanish story_bed3e3c4:

    # "However, my hand hits a wall."
    "Sin embargo, mi mano choca contra una pared."

# game/story.rpy:223
translate spanish story_7c194654:

    # "What the hell!?"
    "¡¿Qué narices?!"

# game/story.rpy:224
translate spanish story_3bddf592:

    # "Okay, deep breaths...deep breaths..."
    "Vale, respira hondo... Respira hondo..."

# game/story.rpy:225
translate spanish story_ee879f7b:

    # "My right hand finally lands on something that feels like a phone on what I assume is a nightstand on my right, only it isn't my smartphone but a flip phone."
    "Finalmente, mi mano derecha se posa sobre algo que parece un móvil en lo que supongo que es una mesita de noche a mi derecha. El caso es que no es mi móvil, sino un mierda de estas de tapa."

# game/story.rpy:226
translate spanish story_814fadcb:

    # "I open it. The alarm is coming from the phone."
    "Lo abro. La alarma proviene del móvil."

# game/story.rpy:228
translate spanish story_e6275987:

    # "I turn it off then use it as a light to help me look around the room."
    "Lo apago y lo uso a modo de linterna para echar un vistazo a la habitación."

# game/story.rpy:234
translate spanish story_9898cbb3:

    # "...What...?"
    "¿Qué...?"

# game/story.rpy:235
translate spanish story_c76b01a4:

    # "This isn't my room!"
    "¡Esta no es mi habitación!"

# game/story.rpy:236
translate spanish story_635353eb:

    # "But there's something familiar about it."
    "Pero me resulta familiar por algún motivo."

# game/story.rpy:237
translate spanish story_92f451bf:

    # "I get out of bed and almost fall flat on my face."
    "Me levanto de la cama y casi me caigo de bruces."

# game/story.rpy:238
translate spanish story_b9029dad:

    # "Why does my body feel lighter?"
    "¿Por qué noto el cuerpo más ligero?"

# game/story.rpy:239
translate spanish story_a64fa5c1:

    # "I stumble over to the door and hit the lightswitch, blinking the light out of my eyes."
    "Me acerco a trompicones a la puerta y le doy al interruptor. Parpadeo para acostumbrarme a la luz."

# game/story.rpy:244
translate spanish story_2b35b6fe:

    # mc "..."
    mc "..."

# game/story.rpy:245
translate spanish story_0af27e43:

    # mc "Oh, you've got to be kidding me! This is the MC's room!"
    mc "Ah, ¡tienes que estar jodiendo! ¡Esta es la habitación de MC!"

# game/story.rpy:246
translate spanish story_d6b9173f:

    # "It's been a while since I've played {i}Doki Doki Literature Club{/i}."
    "Hacía tiempo que no jugaba a {i}Doki Doki Literature Club{/i}."

# game/story.rpy:247
translate spanish story_2cbc2bdf:

    # "I did play a few mods, look up alternate routes, even tried for the good ending..."
    "Jugué a algunos mods, busqué rutas alternativas e incluso intenté sacar el final bueno..."

# game/story.rpy:248
translate spanish story_e5ab1bea:

    # "What a game...geez."
    "Menudo juego... Madre mía."

# game/story.rpy:249
translate spanish story_dd639a86:

    # "I still can't listen to Monika's song without tearing up, though."
    "Aun así, sigo sin poder escuchar la canción de Monika sin soltar una lagrimita masculina."

# game/story.rpy:250
translate spanish story_344c0fcf:

    # "Wait...the MC's room didn't have a window, right?"
    "Un momento... La habitación de MC no tenía ventana, ¿verdad?"

# game/story.rpy:251
translate spanish story_a8a64a46:

    # "Ah! That's not important right now!"
    "¡Ah! ¡Eso no importa ahora!"

# game/story.rpy:252
translate spanish story_0de377df:

    # "I approach the door cautiously, slowly opening it."
    "Me acerco a la puerta con cautela y la abro despacio."

# game/story.rpy:257
translate spanish story_2b35b6fe_1:

    # mc "..."
    mc "..."

# game/story.rpy:258
translate spanish story_dabe3501:

    # "Okay, looks like I'm on the second floor. Not surprised."
    "Vale, parece que estoy en la planta de arriba. No me extraña."

# game/story.rpy:259
translate spanish story_38626531:

    # "What's that room with the small window?"
    "¿Qué es esa habitación con la ventana pequeña?"

# game/story.rpy:264
translate spanish story_2719c5c0:

    # "Perfect! A room with a mirror!"
    "¡Perfecto! ¡Una habitación con espejo!"

# game/story.rpy:269
translate spanish story_2d132510:

    # "I turn on the light."
    "Enciendo la luz."

# game/story.rpy:271
translate spanish story_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/story.rpy:272
translate spanish story_54c6271e:

    # "...What the hell...?"
    "¿Qué narices...?"

# game/story.rpy:273
translate spanish story_a9642d5e:

    # "I don't look like this!"
    "¡Este no soy yo!"

# game/story.rpy:274
translate spanish story_ba38a584:

    # "Who am I looking at?!"
    "¡¿A quién estoy mirando?!"

# game/story.rpy:277
translate spanish story_1a1f2ac9:

    # "I almost shout in shock, but I remember at just the last minute to keep my voice down."
    "Casi pego un grito del susto, pero en el último momento recuerdo que debo hablar bajo."

# game/story.rpy:282
translate spanish story_5217903a:

    # "I turn off the light and head back into the hallway."
    "Apago la luz y vuelvo al pasillo."

# game/story.rpy:287
translate spanish story_c8907aee:

    # "I see two other rooms and a door that looks like it leads to a balcony."
    "Veo otras dos habitaciones y una puerta que parece dar a un balcón."

# game/story.rpy:288
translate spanish story_e26623b4:

    # "I hear soft breathing from one of the rooms."
    "Oigo una respiración suave que proviene de una de las habitaciones."

# game/story.rpy:289
translate spanish story_e7b04544:

    # mc "...Whose rooms are these?"
    mc "¿De quién son estas habitaciones?"

# game/story.rpy:290
translate spanish story_17799653:

    # "I pause."
    "Me detengo."

# game/story.rpy:291
translate spanish story_f5149a98:

    # "That wasn't English...that sounds like...Japanese?"
    "Eso no era español... Eso suena a... ¿japonés?"

# game/story.rpy:292
translate spanish story_1e8cd329:

    # "I know what Japanese sounds like since I watch anime."
    "Sé cómo suena el japonés de tanto ver anime."

# game/story.rpy:293
translate spanish story_be6b27c5:

    # mc "Do I know Japanese somehow?"
    mc "¿Acaso sé hablar japonés?"

# game/story.rpy:294
translate spanish story_a4298500:

    # "That {i}definitely{/i} wasn't English."
    "Desde luego, eso no era español."

# game/story.rpy:295
translate spanish story_bbd9cd52:

    # "I clear my throat softly and try saying something in English."
    "Me aclaro un poco la garganta e intento decir algo en español."

# game/story.rpy:296
translate spanish story_927bdcac:

    # mc "Testing...{w=0.5}one...{w=0.5}two...{w=0.5}three..."
    mc "Probando... {w=0.5}uno... {w=0.5}dos... {w=0.5}tres..."

# game/story.rpy:297
translate spanish story_0ca73795:

    # "Thank God, looks like that worked."
    "Gracias a Dios, parece que ha funcionado."

# game/story.rpy:298
translate spanish story_13206f95:

    # "I try switching back to Japanese."
    "Intento volver a cambiar al japonés."

# game/story.rpy:299
translate spanish story_b29b47ab:

    # mc "Testing...{w=0.5}one...{w=0.5}two...{w=0.5}three."
    mc "Probando... {w=0.5}uno... {w=0.5}dos... {w=0.5}tres."

# game/story.rpy:300
translate spanish story_4cdad7d3:

    # "I stop and think. It seems as if I can switch between languages without any problems."
    "Me detengo y reflexiono. Da la impresión de que puedo cambiar de un idioma a otro sin problema."

# game/story.rpy:301
translate spanish story_aded5c42:

    # "But now I'm freaking out. When did I learn a completely new language?"
    "Pero ahora mismo estoy flipando. ¿En qué momento he aprendido un idioma completamente nuevo?"

# game/story.rpy:302
translate spanish story_42c83178:

    # "And does that mean I'm in Japan somehow?"
    "¿Significa eso que, de algún modo, he acabado en Japón?"

# game/story.rpy:303
translate spanish story_7b421ed6:

    # "I mean, this house does feel a bit like a Japanese house."
    "A ver, esta casa tiene un aire bastante japonés."

# game/story.rpy:304
translate spanish story_e46d5b16:

    # "I rub my forehead."
    "Me froto la frente."

# game/story.rpy:305
translate spanish story_0f310654:

    # "My head feels like it's twice as heavy as it was before."
    "Me pesa la cabeza el doble que antes."

# game/story.rpy:310
translate spanish story_ba4354c1:

    # "Sighing, I smack my cheeks to clear my head."
    "Lanzo un suspiro y me doy unas palmaditas en las mejillas para despejarme."

# game/story.rpy:311
translate spanish story_6055c957:

    # "Exploration comes first."
    "Lo primero es explorar."

# game/story.rpy:312
translate spanish story_5018951d:

    # "I put my ear to the second room's door and, hearing nothing, gently open said door."
    "Pego la oreja a la puerta de la segunda habitación y, al no oír nada, la abro con cuidado."

# game/story.rpy:317
translate spanish story_8e32c7cf:

    # "I open the door and look around briefly. This room most likely belongs to a girl. But who's room is it?"
    "Abro la puerta y echo un vistazo rápido. Esta habitación tiene toda la pinta de pertenecer a una chica. Pero, ¿de quién?"

# game/story.rpy:318
translate spanish story_05253add:

    # "I quickly but quietly leave the room. Somehow I have the feeling that whoever owns this room won't appreciate me snooping."
    "Salgo rápido pero en silencio. Me da a mí que a la dueña de este cuarto no le haría ninguna gracia que ande fisgoneando."

# game/story.rpy:323
translate spanish story_7ae1a8d5:

    # "I walk downstairs and find myself facing a hallway. To the left is a kitchen and to the right is a living room."
    "Bajo las escaleras y llego a un pasillo. A la izquierda está la cocina y, a la derecha, el salón."

# game/story.rpy:328
translate spanish story_5e451d01:

    # "I head into the kitchen first. It's exactly as I remember in the game."
    "Entro primero en la cocina. Es exactamente igual a como la recuerdo del juego."

# game/story.rpy:329
translate spanish story_25d22ff7:

    # "What I don't expect is the large sliding glass door to the left of the fridge."
    "Lo que no me esperaba era encontrar una enorme puerta corredera de cristal a la izquierda de la nevera."

# game/story.rpy:334
translate spanish story_490f98be:

    # "I head back to the hallway and look at the first two doors."
    "Vuelvo al pasillo y me fijo en las dos primeras puertas."

# game/story.rpy:339
translate spanish story_a55f39b5:

    # "Another toilet? I don't know much about Japanese house design, but to have two toilets, MC's parents must be well off."
    "¿Otro retrete? No sé mucho sobre el diseño de las casas japonesas, pero para tener dos, los padres de MC deben de tener bastante pasta."

# game/story.rpy:340
translate spanish story_013cbe3f:

    # "I head to the other room."
    "Me acerco a la otra habitación."

# game/story.rpy:345
translate spanish story_34b8ae1d:

    # "Shower room, of course. A pretty nice one too."
    "La ducha, por supuesto. Y una bastante chula."

# game/story.rpy:346
translate spanish story_13b9c1ff:

    # "What's in the other room?"
    "¿Y qué habrá en la otra habitación?"

# game/story.rpy:351
translate spanish story_cc30a737:

    # "Hmmm...alright, a pretty good sized bath."
    "Mmm... Vale, una bañera de un tamaño considerable."

# game/story.rpy:352
translate spanish story_06252a99:

    # "Deep too."
    "Y bastante profunda."

# game/story.rpy:353
translate spanish story_6ef61626:

    # "If what I know of Japanese houses is right, this is fairly typical."
    "Si no me equivoco con las casas japonesas, esto es bastante típico."

# game/story.rpy:358
translate spanish story_fd7c0ecb:

    # "The door at the end of the hallway is a simple closet with a shelf and a few odds and ends hanging up."
    "Tras la puerta del final del pasillo hay un simple armario con una balda y un par de trastos colgados."

# game/story.rpy:359
translate spanish story_11e7b676:

    # "The door on the left leads down to a basement. I decide to explore that later."
    "La puerta de la izquierda lleva a un sótano. Decido que ya lo exploraré más tarde."

# game/story.rpy:364
translate spanish story_6006062f:

    # "Huh, spare bedroom? Guest room?"
    "Vaya. ¿Un dormitorio libre? ¿Un cuarto de invitados?"

# game/story.rpy:365
translate spanish story_5917d0bd:

    # "Maybe..."
    "Puede ser..."

# game/story.rpy:370
translate spanish story_a55eb8b8:

    # "I turn on the lights."
    "Enciendo la luz."

# game/story.rpy:371
translate spanish story_c34e4382:

    # mc "Huh. Wonder if this is an office or a spare bedroom?"
    mc "Vaya. Me pregunto si esto es un despacho o un dormitorio libre."

# game/story.rpy:376
translate spanish story_ca092c84:

    # "I turn off the light and leave, closing the door quietly."
    "Apago la luz y salgo, cerrando la puerta en silencio."

# game/story.rpy:381
translate spanish story_34e2f97e:

    # "The living room is the largest room I've seen so far."
    "El salón es la sala más grande que he visto hasta ahora."

# game/story.rpy:382
translate spanish story_9fd929d1:

    # "The digital clock on the DVD player says 4:12 AM."
    "El reloj del reproductor de DVD marca las 4:12 de la madrugada."

# game/story.rpy:383
translate spanish story_58303935:

    # "From upstairs I hear a door open. A light turns on."
    "Oigo que se abre una puerta en el piso de arriba. Se enciende una luz."

# game/story.rpy:389
translate spanish story_1783a61d:

    # u "Meiji? Is that you?"
    u "¿Meiji? ¿Eres tú?"

# game/story.rpy:390
translate spanish story_92f933ba:

    # "A mature sounding female voice calls down the stairs."
    "La voz madura de una mujer me llama desde lo alto de las escaleras."

# game/story.rpy:391
translate spanish story_044b074c:

    # "I'm guessing the MC is Meiji?"
    "Supongo que el protagonista se llama Meiji, ¿no?"

# game/story.rpy:392
translate spanish story_9ced73c4:

    # "But...I didn't choose that name when I played DDLC. So why that name?"
    "Pero... no es el nombre que yo elegí cuando jugué a DDLC. Así que, ¿a qué viene ese nombre?"

# game/story.rpy:393
translate spanish story_324a86b6:

    # "Am I not in the MC's body?"
    "¿Acaso no estoy en el cuerpo de MC?"

# game/story.rpy:399
translate spanish story_95921924:

    # "I walk upstairs."
    "Subo las escaleras."

# game/story.rpy:400
translate spanish story_665792ba:

    # "Huh, I wonder who this woman is?"
    "Hala, ¿y quién será esta mujer?"

# game/story.rpy:401
translate spanish story_2d71d111:

    # "I'm guessing this is the Mom of the person I saw in the mirror? Well, best not to assume."
    "Supongo que es la madre del chico que vi en el espejo... Bueno, mejor no dar nada por sentado."

# game/story.rpy:402
translate spanish story_3e3544bd:

    # "Time to bluff my way through this."
    "Toca ir de farol y salir del paso."

# game/story.rpy:403
translate spanish story_47f36e72:

    # "The woman approaches me worriedly."
    "La mujer se me acerca con cara de preocupación."

# game/story.rpy:405
translate spanish story_550ce1f0:

    # u "Are you feeling okay, Meiji?"
    u "¿Te encuentras bien, Meiji?"

# game/story.rpy:406
translate spanish story_aab50c83:

    # "So I {i}am{/i} inside this Meiji's body."
    "Así que sí que estoy en el cuerpo de este tal Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:407
translate spanish story_e79df68d:

    # mc "I'm fine."
    mc "Estoy bien."

# game/story.rpy:408
translate spanish story_4769f029:

    # mc "I just had a nightmare and was going to get a glass of water."
    mc "Acabo de tener una pesadilla e iba a buscar un vaso de agua."

# game/story.rpy:409
translate spanish story_2c644874:

    # "From behind the woman I hear shuffling. A man walks out."
    "Oigo unos pasos detrás de la mujer. Entonces, aparece un hombre."

# game/story.rpy:412
translate spanish story_a1274c99:

    # "Meiji's dad I'm guessing?"
    "El padre de Meiji, supongo."

# game/story.rpy:414
translate spanish story_59963497:

    # u "What's going on out there, Minako?"
    u "¿Qué pasa ahí fuera, Minako?"

# game/story.rpy:416
translate spanish story_fda15e43:

    # u "Wait, Meiji? Why are you up so early, son?"
    u "Un momento, ¿Meiji? ¿A qué viene madrugar tanto, hijo?"

# game/story.rpy:418
translate spanish story_3173b614:

    # "Guess that confirms that. This has to be Meiji's dad."
    "Supongo que eso lo confirma. Este tiene que ser el padre de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:420
translate spanish story_ee749783:

    # u "He had a nightmare, Tatsuo."
    u "Ha tenido una pesadilla, Tatsuo."

# game/story.rpy:422
translate spanish story_af96a1e4:

    # u "Meiji, I'll get you a glass of water. You just go to bed."
    u "Meiji, iré a buscarte ese vaso de agua. Tú vuelve a la cama."

# game/story.rpy:424
translate spanish story_71f5aa09:

    # mc "Um...alright."
    mc "Mmm... Vale."

# game/story.rpy:425
translate spanish story_54c71ebd:

    # "And I guess this makes this woman Meiji's mom."
    "Y supongo que eso convierte a esta mujer en la madre de Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:434
translate spanish story_e390de94:

    # "I head back in and sit on the edge of the bed. Meiji's mom comes in a bit later with a glass of cold water, which I drink gratefully. She sits next to me."
    "Vuelvo al cuarto y me siento en el borde de la cama. La madre de Meiji entra poco después con un vaso de agua fría, el cual bebo agradecido."

# game/story.rpy:436
translate spanish story_9683f264:

    # mom "Want to tell me about your dream?"
    mom "¿Quieres contarme qué has soñado?"

# game/story.rpy:438
translate spanish story_a2cbde33:

    # "I shrug, trying to remember how teenage me would act."
    "Me encojo de hombros, intentando recordar cómo me habría comportado siendo adolescente."

# game/story.rpy:439
translate spanish story_8579f06b:

    # "It wasn't so long ago for me, after all. But for some reason it's hard to remember."
    "Al fin y al cabo, no hace tanto tiempo de aquello. Pero, por algún motivo, me cuesta recordarlo."

# game/story.rpy:440
translate spanish story_e6015101:

    # mc "It's okay, Mom. I can't really remember anything about it."
    mc "No pasa nada, mamá. La verdad es que casi no me acuerdo de nada."

# game/story.rpy:441
translate spanish story_c2f3f85b:

    # "Ugh, I can't act for shit!"
    "Buf, ¡qué asco doy actuando!"

# game/story.rpy:442
translate spanish story_5215c83e:

    # mom 5ph "You sure? You look a bit pale."
    mom 5ph "¿Seguro? Estás un poco pálido."

# game/story.rpy:444
translate spanish story_86e78269:

    # "I nearly jump back as this woman presses her forehead to mine."
    "Casi doy un respingo cuando esta mujer me planta su frente contra la mía."

# game/story.rpy:445
translate spanish story_e4cbb5a4:

    # mom 1pf "You're not sick or anything."
    mom 1pf "Parece que no estás enfermo."

# game/story.rpy:447
translate spanish story_1d53998c:

    # "Startled, I move back a bit."
    "Sorprendido, me echo un poco hacia atrás."

# game/story.rpy:449
translate spanish story_3292bc53:

    # mom "Meiji?"
    mom "¿Meiji?"

# game/story.rpy:451
translate spanish story_055f7242:

    # mc "Ah, um..."
    mc "Ah... Eh..."

# game/story.rpy:452
translate spanish story_9ad43776:

    # "Ugh, try and act like a teenager, me! How would one react?"
    "Jo, ¡concéntrate en actuar como un adolescente! ¿Cómo reaccionaría uno?"

# game/story.rpy:453
translate spanish story_6981781d:

    # mc "I'm really okay. I'm just tired."
    mc "De verdad que estoy bien. Solo estoy cansado."

# game/story.rpy:454
translate spanish story_2c9c4a35:

    # "I try to make my words sound sleepy. And that's not hard, considering it's so early in the morning."
    "Intento que mi voz suene adormilada. Tampoco es muy difícil, teniendo en cuenta lo temprano que es."

# game/story.rpy:455
translate spanish story_9170104b:

    # mom 2pk "Well, alright. If you're sure."
    mom 2pk "Vale, de acuerdo. Si estás seguro..."

# game/story.rpy:456
translate spanish story_54193b93:

    # mom 5pb "You should sleep dear. It is the weekend still, after all."
    mom 5pb "Deberías dormir, cielo. Después de todo, aún es fin de semana."

# game/story.rpy:458
translate spanish story_05a2913a:

    # mc "Right, sorry for waking you."
    mc "Vale, perdón por despertarte."

# game/story.rpy:459
translate spanish story_cca968a7:

    # mom 4pc "It's okay."
    mom 4pc "No pasa nada."

# game/story.rpy:460
translate spanish story_c934b35b:

    # mom 1pa "Now go to sleep, sweetie. See you in the morning."
    mom 1pa "Ahora a dormir, cariño. Nos vemos por la mañana."

# game/story.rpy:461
translate spanish story_f2c15ce7:

    # mc "Alright. Night."
    mc "Vale. Buenas noches."

# game/story.rpy:462
translate spanish story_34664eab:

    # mom 1pb "Goodnight, Meiji."
    mom 1pb "Buenas noches, Meiji."

# game/story.rpy:467
translate spanish story_6a68466b:

    # "She turns off the light and I lie down on the bed."
    "Apaga la luz y me acuesto en la cama."

# game/story.rpy:472
translate spanish story_38e042f3:

    # "I close my eyes and let my mind wander."
    "Cierro los ojos y dejo vagar la mente."

# game/story.rpy:473
translate spanish story_865ac25f:

    # "I start thinking about my current situation."
    "Empiezo a pensar en mi situación actual."

# game/story.rpy:474
translate spanish story_f3d5b1d4:

    # mc "{b}I'm freaking out...This has {i}GOT{/i} to be a very elaborate dream.{/b}"
    mc "{i}Estoy flipando... Esto tiene que ser un sueño muy elaborado.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:475
translate spanish story_bb8b41f9:

    # mc "{b}I mean first, to wake up in the MC's room-{/b}"
    mc "{i}O sea, para empezar, despertarme en la habitación del prota...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:476
translate spanish story_d0a53a59:

    # u "{i}No, this is my room, and who the hell are you?!{/i}"
    u "{i}No, esta es mi habitación. ¡¿Y quién narices eres tú?!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:482
translate spanish story_2215566e:

    # "I sit up quickly and look around. Someone had just shouted in my ear. I tilt my head in confusion."
    "Me incorporo de golpe y miro a mi alrededor. Alguien me acaba de gritar en la oreja. Ladeo la cabeza, confundido."

# game/story.rpy:483
translate spanish story_c6819c0e:

    # mc "Who said that?"
    mc "¿Quién ha dicho eso?"

# game/story.rpy:484
translate spanish story_c653e4ea:

    # u "{i}I did! What's going on? Why can't I move?{/i}"
    u "{i}¡He sido yo! ¿Qué está pasando? ¿Por qué no puedo moverme?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:485
translate spanish story_82d68200:

    # "The voice sounds terrified. It also sounds like my new voice. It's coming from my head, like some kind of audible thought. Realization sets in."
    "La voz suena aterrorizada, y también suena como mi nueva voz. Proviene de mi propia cabeza, como si fuera un pensamiento audible. De repente, caigo en la cuenta."

# game/story.rpy:486
translate spanish story_71656994:

    # mc "Hold up, are you...Meiji?"
    mc "Un momento, ¿eres... Meiji?"

# game/story.rpy:487
translate spanish story_e1386653:

    # cm "{i}Damn right I am! Who the hell are you!?{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡Pues claro que sí! ¡¿Y quién narices eres tú?!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:488
translate spanish story_cdcb8e9c:

    # "I lie back down."
    "Vuelvo a acostarme."

# game/story.rpy:489
translate spanish story_b89bc6c9:

    # mc "Listen, I'm sure you're freaking out a lot, but it's nothing compared to how I'm feeling."
    mc "Escucha, seguro que estás flipando mucho, pero no es nada comparado con cómo me siento yo."

# game/story.rpy:490
translate spanish story_270bfbed:

    # "I should tell him my name."
    "Debería decirle mi nombre."

# game/story.rpy:491
translate spanish story_3b6aac38:

    # mc "I'm [fname] [lname], by the way. I'm from America."
    mc "Por cierto, soy [fname] [lname]. Soy de Estados Unidos."

# game/story.rpy:492
translate spanish story_1a528f33:

    # cm "{i}Chizu Meiji. Now seriously, what the hell is going on?! You have control of my body, how are you any more terrified than I am!?{/i}"
    cm "{i}Yo soy Chizu Meiji. Ahora en serio, ¡¿qué narices está pasando?! Tienes el control de mi cuerpo, ¡¿cómo vas a estar más aterrorizado que yo?!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:493
translate spanish story_17fe3418:

    # "He sounds even more scared than I feel."
    "Suena aún más asustado de lo que yo me siento."

# game/story.rpy:494
translate spanish story_cd857785:

    # "Getting him to calm down isn't going to be easy, but I have to do this."
    "No va a ser fácil conseguir que se calme, pero tengo que hacerlo."

# game/story.rpy:495
translate spanish story_087a528a:

    # "I take a few deep breaths to try and calm myself down first. Finally, I'm ready."
    "Respiro hondo un par de veces para intentar calmarme primero. Por fin, estoy listo."

# game/story.rpy:496
translate spanish story_21440761:

    # mc "If you want to know, just calm down and I'll tell you."
    mc "Si quieres saberlo, cálmate y te lo contaré."

# game/story.rpy:497
translate spanish story_642dd67d:

    # cm "{i}Calm?! HOW CAN I BE CALM! I'm trapped in my own--{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡¿Que me calme?! ¡¿CÓMO VOY A CALMARME?! Estoy atrapado en mi propio...{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:503
translate spanish story_1b88f674:

    # "SMACK!"
    "¡ZAS!"

# game/story.rpy:504
translate spanish story_98f79e04:

    # "My cheek stings from my self-inflicted slap."
    "Me escuece la mejilla por la bofetada que me acabo de dar."

# game/story.rpy:505
translate spanish story_df708b8c:

    # mc "Calm. Down."
    mc "Cálmate. Ya."

# game/story.rpy:506
translate spanish story_95c3c840:

    # cm "..."
    cm "..."

# game/story.rpy:507
translate spanish story_31f36fd0:

    # cm "{i}Damn it...I felt that.{/i}"
    cm "{i}Maldita sea... Eso lo he sentido.{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:508
translate spanish story_11d90d0c:

    # mc "Good. Now just take a few deep breaths, alright? It's not doing us any good just panicking."
    mc "Bien. Ahora respira hondo un par de veces, ¿vale? Entrar en pánico no nos sirve de nada."

# game/story.rpy:509
translate spanish story_8021a089:

    # cm "{i}How the hell are you so calm??{/i}"
    cm "{i}¡¿Cómo narices puedes estar tan tranquilo?!{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:510
translate spanish story_3e35c98c:

    # mc "I'm not. I'm just as freaked out as you are, trust me."
    mc "No lo estoy. Te juro que estoy igual de asustado que tú."

# game/story.rpy:511
translate spanish story_669a76b8:

    # mc "Let's just take a few moments."
    mc "Vamos a tomarnos un respiro."

# game/story.rpy:512
translate spanish story_95c3c840_1:

    # cm "..."
    cm "..."

# game/story.rpy:513
translate spanish story_9d3ce645:

    # "I lie back down on the bed and breathe normally, trying to let my own racing mind slow down."
    "Vuelvo a recostarme en la cama y respiro con normalidad, intentando que mi mente a mil por hora se calme."

# game/story.rpy:514
translate spanish story_0b4c840f:

    # "Slowly, my heartbeat returns to a somewhat more normal rate. Not that I know what the normal heartrate for his body is."
    "Poco a poco, mis latidos vuelven a un ritmo algo más normal. Aunque tampoco es que sepa cuál es el ritmo normal de su cuerpo."

# game/story.rpy:515
translate spanish story_bfc298a5:

    # cm "{i}Alright. So, I guess I'm not going crazy?{/i}"
    cm "{i}Vale. Entonces, ¿supongo que no me estoy volviendo loco?{/i}"

# game/story.rpy:516
translate spanish story_70d25006:

    # "I slowly shake my head and sit back up. I lean against the wall."
    "Niego lentamente con la cabeza y me vuelvo a incorporar. Me apoyo contra la pared."

# game/story.rpy:517
